title: About Me
text:
Hello everyone! My name is John and I am a Math Major (Stats Emphasis) student at California State University Channel Islands.



I enjoy learning new things, spending time with friends and family, and good food!
I am passionate about Artificial Intelligence. Specifically unsupervised learning.
I am currently learning how to utilize non-negative matrix factorization and polyadic decomposition.

Thank you for visiting my site!
